room_title: Escape room "Blackout" by The Final Door in Columbia
review: Just did the Blackout room. It was an awesome time. Gamemaster Danny was great! I'm looking forward to my next visit!

room_title: Escape room "Blackout" by The Final Door in Columbia
review: It was totally awesome I was scared out of my mind... They did an awesome job with making sure we got the full experience of the blackout theme. Definitely will be going back to do the vampire!

room_title: Escape room "Blackout" by The Final Door in Columbia
review: We did the Blackout room with Danny as our game master and we had a fantastic time! Can't wait to go back for the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Blackout" by The Final Door in Columbia
review: We were a group of three, two newbies and one escape room veteran and all three of us had a blast! The Blackout room was so well put together, and our game masters Tyler & Danny were great. Can't wait to do another one here!
